<p><strong>1.&nbsp;Introduction</strong></p><p>Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;(“we,”&nbsp;“our,”&nbsp;“us”)&nbsp;respects&nbsp;your&nbsp;privacy&nbsp;and&nbsp;is&nbsp;committed&nbsp;to&nbsp;protecting&nbsp;your&nbsp;data.&nbsp;This&nbsp;Privacy&nbsp;Policy&nbsp;explains&nbsp;how&nbsp;we&nbsp;collect,&nbsp;use,&nbsp;and&nbsp;protect&nbsp;your&nbsp;information&nbsp;when&nbsp;you&nbsp;use&nbsp;our&nbsp;website&nbsp;and&nbsp;services.</p><p></p><p><strong>2.&nbsp;Information&nbsp;We&nbsp;Collect</strong></p><p>A.&nbsp;Data&nbsp;You&nbsp;Provide:</p><p>-&nbsp;Name,&nbsp;email,&nbsp;phone&nbsp;number,&nbsp;company&nbsp;name</p><p>-&nbsp;Billing&nbsp;and&nbsp;payment&nbsp;details&nbsp;(processed&nbsp;securely&nbsp;via&nbsp;Stripe&nbsp;or&nbsp;similar&nbsp;processors)</p><p>-&nbsp;Message&nbsp;content&nbsp;and&nbsp;contact&nbsp;lists&nbsp;you&nbsp;upload</p><p>-&nbsp;Support&nbsp;requests&nbsp;and&nbsp;communication</p><p></p><p>B.&nbsp;Automatically&nbsp;Collected&nbsp;Data:</p><p>-&nbsp;IP&nbsp;address,&nbsp;browser,&nbsp;and&nbsp;device&nbsp;info</p><p>-&nbsp;Access&nbsp;times,&nbsp;referral&nbsp;URLs,&nbsp;and&nbsp;session&nbsp;duration</p><p>-&nbsp;Cookies&nbsp;and&nbsp;analytics&nbsp;tools</p><p></p><p><strong>3.&nbsp;How&nbsp;We&nbsp;Use&nbsp;Your&nbsp;Data</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;use&nbsp;your&nbsp;data&nbsp;to:</p><p>-&nbsp;Operate&nbsp;and&nbsp;improve&nbsp;the&nbsp;platform</p><p>-&nbsp;Process&nbsp;billing&nbsp;and&nbsp;message&nbsp;delivery</p><p>-&nbsp;Provide&nbsp;customer&nbsp;support</p><p>-&nbsp;Prevent&nbsp;abuse&nbsp;and&nbsp;ensure&nbsp;compliance</p><p>-&nbsp;Send&nbsp;service-related&nbsp;updates&nbsp;or&nbsp;promotional&nbsp;messages&nbsp;(opt-out&nbsp;available)</p><p></p><p><strong>4.&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Sharing&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Disclosure</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;may&nbsp;share&nbsp;your&nbsp;information&nbsp;with:</p><p>-&nbsp;Carriers&nbsp;and&nbsp;delivery&nbsp;partners&nbsp;for&nbsp;message&nbsp;routing</p><p>-&nbsp;Payment&nbsp;processors&nbsp;(e.g.,&nbsp;Stripe)</p><p>-&nbsp;Legal&nbsp;authorities&nbsp;when&nbsp;required</p><p>We&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;sell&nbsp;or&nbsp;rent&nbsp;personal&nbsp;data&nbsp;to&nbsp;third&nbsp;parties.</p><p></p><p><strong>5.&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Security&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Retention</strong></p><p>Data&nbsp;is&nbsp;encrypted&nbsp;during&nbsp;transmission&nbsp;and&nbsp;stored&nbsp;securely.&nbsp;Access&nbsp;is&nbsp;limited&nbsp;to&nbsp;authorized&nbsp;personnel.&nbsp;We&nbsp;retain&nbsp;information&nbsp;only&nbsp;as&nbsp;long&nbsp;as&nbsp;necessary&nbsp;for&nbsp;legitimate&nbsp;or&nbsp;legal&nbsp;purposes.</p><p></p><p><strong>6.&nbsp;Your&nbsp;Rights</strong></p><p>Depending&nbsp;on&nbsp;your&nbsp;jurisdiction,&nbsp;you&nbsp;may:</p><p>-&nbsp;Request&nbsp;access,&nbsp;correction,&nbsp;or&nbsp;deletion&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;data</p><p>-&nbsp;Withdraw&nbsp;consent&nbsp;to&nbsp;processing</p><p>-&nbsp;File&nbsp;complaints&nbsp;regarding&nbsp;data&nbsp;handling</p><p>Requests&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;sent&nbsp;to&nbsp;privacy@groupdm.net.</p><p></p><p><strong>7.&nbsp;Cookies&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Tracking</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;use&nbsp;cookies&nbsp;and&nbsp;analytics&nbsp;to&nbsp;enhance&nbsp;performance&nbsp;and&nbsp;improve&nbsp;user&nbsp;experience.&nbsp;You&nbsp;can&nbsp;disable&nbsp;cookies&nbsp;in&nbsp;your&nbsp;browser&nbsp;settings,&nbsp;but&nbsp;some&nbsp;features&nbsp;may&nbsp;not&nbsp;function&nbsp;properly.</p><p></p><p><strong>8.&nbsp;Children’s&nbsp;Privacy</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;knowingly&nbsp;collect&nbsp;or&nbsp;store&nbsp;data&nbsp;from&nbsp;anyone&nbsp;under&nbsp;13.&nbsp;If&nbsp;such&nbsp;data&nbsp;is&nbsp;discovered,&nbsp;it&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;deleted&nbsp;promptly.</p><p></p><p><strong>9.&nbsp;International&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Transfers</strong></p><p>If&nbsp;you&nbsp;access&nbsp;our&nbsp;platform&nbsp;outside&nbsp;the&nbsp;U.S.,&nbsp;you&nbsp;agree&nbsp;that&nbsp;your&nbsp;data&nbsp;may&nbsp;be&nbsp;processed&nbsp;and&nbsp;stored&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;U.S.&nbsp;in&nbsp;compliance&nbsp;with&nbsp;applicable&nbsp;laws.</p><p></p><p><strong>10.&nbsp;Updates&nbsp;to&nbsp;This&nbsp;Policy</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;may&nbsp;revise&nbsp;this&nbsp;Privacy&nbsp;Policy&nbsp;at&nbsp;any&nbsp;time.&nbsp;Continued&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;our&nbsp;services&nbsp;constitutes&nbsp;acceptance&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;revised&nbsp;version.</p><p></p><p><strong>11.&nbsp;Contact&nbsp;Us</strong></p><p>For&nbsp;privacy-related&nbsp;inquiries,&nbsp;contact&nbsp;privacy@groupdm.net.</p><p></p>